input: what was the name of the drug prescribed to patient 015-23047, two times in their current hospital visit?
predict:
select t1.drugname from medication t1
join patient t2 on t1.patientunitstayid = t2.patientunitstayid
where t2.uniquepid = '015-23047'
  and t1.drugstarttime = ( select max(t3.drugstarttime) from medication t3 where t3.patientunitstayid in ( select patientunitstayid from patient where uniquepid = '015-23047' ) )
group by t1.drugname
having count(*) = 2;
real: select t1.drugname from ( select medication.drugname, count( medication.drugstarttime ) as c1 from medication where medication.patientunitstayid in ( select patient.patientunitstayid from patient where patient.patienthealthsystemstayid in ( select patient.patienthealthsystemstayid from patient where patient.uniquepid = '015-23047' and patient.hospitaldischargetime is null ) ) group by medication.drugname ) as t1 where t1.c1 = 2;

input: what is the prescription that patient 006-77873 has been prescribed two times in the last hospital visit?
predict:
select t1.drugname from (
    select medication.drugname, count(*) as prescription_count from medication
    join patient on medication.patientunitstayid = patient.patientunitstayid
    where patient.uniquepid = '006-77873'
    and patient.hospitaldischargestatus = 'alive'
    group by medication.drugname
    having count(*) = 2
) as t1;
real: select t1.drugname from ( select medication.drugname, count( medication.drugstarttime ) as c1 from medication where medication.patientunitstayid in ( select patient.patientunitstayid from patient where patient.patienthealthsystemstayid in ( select patient.patienthealthsystemstayid from patient where patient.uniquepid = '006-77873' and patient.hospitaldischargetime is not null order by patient.hospitaladmittime desc limit 1 ) ) group by medication.drugname ) as t1 where t1.c1 = 2;

input: what is the drug that patient 006-105495 has been prescribed two times in the current hospital visit?
predict:
select t1.drugname from medication t1
join patient t2 on t1.patientunitstayid = t2.patientunitstayid
where t2.uniquepid = '006-105495'
  and t1.drugstarttime >= t2.hospitaladmittime
  and t1.drugstarttime <= datetime(t2.hospitaladmittime,'start of day')
group by t1.drugname
having count(*) = 2;
real: select t1.drugname from ( select medication.drugname, count( medication.drugstarttime ) as c1 from medication where medication.patientunitstayid in ( select patient.patientunitstayid from patient where patient.patienthealthsystemstayid in ( select patient.patienthealthsystemstayid from patient where patient.uniquepid = '006-105495' and patient.hospitaldischargetime is null ) ) group by medication.drugname ) as t1 where t1.c1 = 2;

input: what was the survival rate of patients diagnosed with hepatic dysfunction - liver transplant for a time of one year?
predict: select count(*) * 100.0 / (select count(*) from patient where patient.hospitaldischargestatus = 'alive' and patient.unitdischargetime is not null and datetime(patient.unitdischargetime) >= datetime('2105-12-31 23:59:00', '-1 year')) from patient join diagnosis on patient.patientunitstayid = diagnosis.patientunitstayid where diagnosis.diagnosisname = 'hepatic dysfunction - liver transplant' and patient.hospitaldischargestatus = 'alive' and patient.unitdischargetime is not null and datetime(patient.unitdischargetime) >= datetime('2105-12-31 23:59:00', '-1 year'));
real: select sum( case when patient.hospitaldischargestatus = 'alive' then 1 when strftime('%J',patient.hospitaldischargetime) - strftime('%J',t2.diagnosistime) > 1 * 365 then 1 else 0 end ) * 100 / count(*) from ( select t1.uniquepid, t1.diagnosistime from ( select patient.uniquepid, diagnosis.diagnosistime from diagnosis join patient on diagnosis.patientunitstayid = patient.patientunitstayid where diagnosis.diagnosisname = 'hepatic dysfunction - liver transplant' group by patient.uniquepid having min(diagnosis.diagnosistime) = diagnosis.diagnosistime ) as t1 where strftime('%J','2105-12-31 23:59:00') - strftime('%J',t1.diagnosistime) > 1 * 365 ) as t2 join patient on t2.uniquepid = patient.uniquepid;

input: for patients who took physical medicine consultation in this year, what are the top three most common procedures that followed in the same hospital encounter?
predict:
select t3.treatmentname from (
    select patient.patienthealthsystemstayid, treatment.treatmentname, count(*) as procedure_count
    from treatment
    join patient on treatment.patientunitstayid = patient.patientunitstayid
    where treatment.treatmentname = 'physical medicine consultation'
        and datetime(treatment.treatmenttime, 'start of year') = datetime('2105-12-31 23:59:00', 'start of year')
    group by patient.patienthealthsystemstayid, treatment.treatmentname
) as t1
join (
    select patient.patienthealthsystemstayid, treatment.treatmentname, count(*) as procedure_count
    from treatment
    join patient on treatment.patientunitstayid = patient.patientunitstayid
    where datetime(treatment.treatmenttime, 'start of year') = datetime('2105-12-31 23:59:00', 'start of year')
    group by patient.patienthealthsystemstayid, treatment.treatmentname
) as t2 on t1.patienthealthsystemstayid = t2.patienthealthsystemstayid
join (
    select treatment.treatmentname, dense_rank() over (order by count(*) desc) as rank
    from treatment
    join patient on treatment.patientunitstayid = patient.patientunitstayid
    where datetime(treatment.treatmenttime, 'start of year') = datetime('2105-12-31 23:59:00', 'start of year')
    group by treatment.treatmentname
) as t3 on t2.treatmentname = t3.treatmentname
where t3.rank <= 3;

input: what are 10 most recent papers on sepsis - sepsis with single organ dysfunction- metabolic encephalopathy?
predict:
SELECT 
    p.uniquepid, 
    p.patientunitstayid, 
    p.hospitaladmittime, 
    d.diagnosisname, 
    t.treatmentname, 
    l.labname, 
    a.allergyname, 
    m.drugname, 
    io.celllabel, 
    ml.organism 
FROM patient p 
JOIN diagnosis d ON p.patientunitstayid = d.patientunitstayid 
JOIN treatment t ON p.patientunitstayid = t.patientunitstayid 
JOIN lab l ON p.patientunitstayid = l.patientunitstayid 
JOIN allergy a ON p.patientunitstayid = a.patientunitstayid 
JOIN medication m ON p.patientunitstayid = m.patientunitstayid 
JOIN intakeoutput io ON p.patientunitstayid = io.patientunitstayid 
JOIN microlab ml ON p.patientunitstayid = ml.patientunitstayid 
WHERE 
    d.diagnosisname LIKE '%sepsis%' 
    AND d.diagnosisname LIKE '%single organ dysfunction%' 
    AND d.diagnosisname LIKE '%metabolic encephalopathy%' 
ORDER BY 
    p.hospitaladmittime DESC 
LIMIT 10;
